CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, February 14, 1938, pg. 22 reads: "'Trucking On Down.' Lena Horne of the wining smile cuts some fancy steps at the farewell party given in her honor at the Loendi Club Parlors in Pittsburgh last week.  Earl McDonald, D.C. sportsman, and Teddy Horne, Lena's father are looking on."
TitMainTitle: Lena Horne dancing with her husband Louis Jones in Loendi Cub
